OL,3,CPaterson: Five years on, what action
OL,4,Chas been taken to stop criminal
OL,5,Csurgeons?
OL,7,FThree years later an inquiry into the
OL,8,Fscandal was published, which made 15
OL,9,Frecommendations to the government,
OL,10,Fincluding the greater sharing of
OL,11,Finformation between the private and
OL,12,Fpublic sector and better protection
OL,13,Ffor patients by more insurance in
OL,14,Fprivate practice.
OL,16,FNow, half a decade on, I have been
OL,17,Fspeaking to a former patient of Ian
OL,18,FPaterson, and a lawyer who has
OL,19,Frepresented hundreds of those he
OL,20,Ftreated.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
