OL,3,CPaterson: Five years on, what action
OL,4,Chas been taken to stop criminal
OL,5,Csurgeons?
OL,7,FDebbie Douglas and Kashmir Uppal both
OL,8,Fsay that not enough has been done to
OL,9,Fimplement the recommendations.
OL,11,FSince the report in 2020, there has
OL,12,Fbeen one government update on
OL,13,Fprogress, published in 2022 and
OL,14,Fshowing that lots of work was still
OL,15,Fneeded.
OL,17,FSince then there have not been any
OL,18,Fofficial updates.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
