OL,3,CPaterson: Five years on, what action
OL,4,Chas been taken to stop criminal
OL,5,Csurgeons?
OL,7,FTop of Debbie and Kashmir's list of
OL,8,Fconcerns was the recommendation around
OL,9,Fclinical indemnity which said: "We
OL,10,Frecommend that the Government should,
OL,11,Fas a matter of urgency, reform the
OL,12,Fcurrent regulation of indemnity
OL,13,Fproducts for healthcare professionals,
OL,14,Fin light of the serious shortcomings
OL,15,Fidentified by the Inquiry, and
OL,16,Fintroduce a nationwide safety net to
OL,17,Fensure patients are not disadvantaged."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
