OL,3,CPaterson: Five years on, what action
OL,4,Chas been taken to stop criminal
OL,5,Csurgeons?
OL,7,FThat was one of the recommendations
OL,8,Fmade after the the Medical Defence
OL,9,FUnion used its discretion to withdraw
OL,10,Fcover, since Paterson's activity was
OL,11,Fcriminal, leaving patients without
OL,12,Fcover.
OL,14,FDebbie Douglas, the Chair of Breast
OL,15,FFriends Solihull, is concerned that
OL,16,Fnothing has been rectified around this.
OL,18,FShe said: "So a consultant can still
OL,19,Frent a room in a private hospital and
OL,20,Fthat hospital has no cover, there's no
OL,21,Findemnity if it's a criminal act.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
