OL,3,CPaterson: Five years on, what action
OL,4,Chas been taken to stop criminal
OL,5,Csurgeons?
OL,7,F"So like us the patients are left
OL,8,Ffighting for five years for
OL,9,Fcompensation for the harm that was
OL,10,Fcaused."
OL,12,FThat is also of concern to medical
OL,13,Fnegligence lawyer Kashmir, who asked:
OL,14,F"what is the point of having an
OL,15,Finquiry when five years down the line
OL,16,Fso few of the recommendations have
OL,17,Factually been implemented?"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
