OL,3,CPaterson: Five years on, what action
OL,4,Chas been taken to stop criminal
OL,5,Csurgeons?
OL,7,FFor their part, the current government
OL,8,Fis completely different to the
OL,9,Fgovernment who commissioned the report
OL,10,F(Theresa May's administration) and
OL,11,Fthose who published it (Boris
OL,12,FJohnson's).
OL,14,FIt was Rishi Sunak's government which
OL,15,Fpublished the update in 2022 and now
OL,16,Fit is the turn of Sir Keir Starmer's
OL,17,Fadministration to continue
OL,18,Fimplementation.
OL,20,F"We are working urgently"
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
