OL,3,CPaterson: Five years on, what action
OL,4,Chas been taken to stop criminal
OL,5,Csurgeons?
OL,7,FIt is something they have told us they
OL,8,Fare planning to do: "This Government
OL,9,Fhas pledged to bar NHS managers that
OL,10,Fsilence whistleblowers and
OL,11,Fcommissioned Dr Penny Dash to review
OL,12,Fpatient safety across England.
OL,14,F"We are working urgently to implement
OL,15,Fthe remaining Paterson recommendations
OL,16,Fand will put patient safety at the
OL,17,Fheart of our 10 Year Plan for Health."
