OL,3,CPaterson: Five years on, what action
OL,4,Chas been taken to stop criminal
OL,5,Csurgeons?
OL,7,FDebbie Douglas pointed out, though,
OL,8,Fthat implementing the recommendations
OL,9,Fis only half the battle. Making sure
OL,10,Fthere is the governance in place so
OL,11,Fthe recommendations are effective is
OL,12,Fanother.
OL,14,FHopefully that won't take another five
OL,15,Fyears to do.
